 to six months imprisonment after he pleaded guilty to stealing N50,000 from one Olaoye Temitope. October 19, 2015 In "News" An Ota Magistrates’ Court in Ogun on Wednesday sentenced a 29-year-old man, Dotun Akande, to one year in prison for N935.000 belonging to Orisun Microfinance Bank. November 14, 2018 In "News" An Ota Magistrates’ Court in Ogun, on Tuesday sentenced a 21-year-old man, Tunde Kareem to one-year imprisonment for stealing generator parts valued at N15,000. February 28, 2017 In "News"